Interface IExportDeclaration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IJavaScriptElement, ILookupScope, ISourceManipulation, ISourceReference

    public interface IExportDeclaration
extends IJavaScriptElement, ISourceReference, ISourceManipulation
    Represents an export declaration in JavaScript unit.

    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
